data.description: This Pima Villa is on one of the larger lots in sought after Palo Verde. This home sits on a quiet cul-de-sac. It features a beautiful entry way with vaulted ceiling and decorated pillars. Architecture is beautiful. Living room, dining room, cozy family room and half bath off kitchen. Eat in kitchen, granite counter tops, plenty of cabinets.  2 Bedroom and 2.5 baths featuring 2 master suites.    Newer HVAC, roof, and exterior painted.  2 car garage with plenty of storage space.  Plus a golf cart tower space. Come enjoy the sunsets with family and friends.  Plenty of space to entertain in this beautifully desert landscape back yard with covered patio, fountain, fire pit and view of golf course.  A MUST SEE!
